<DOCOLDNO>IA090-000966-B014-397</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.pipes.org:80/BURST/FORMATTED/103.001.html 206.129.190.10 19970208063102 text/html 6170
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
