From: ????????@???.???????.???
Subject: Pipes Digest #123 - December 17, 1993

		Pipes Digest #123 - December 17, 1993

Welcome to new members:

	Larry Finch		(??????????@???.???)
	ghpatrick		(?????????@???.???)
