<body>
<pre>
From: ????????@???.???????.???
Subject: Pipes Digest #130 - February 11, 1994

		Pipes Digest #130 - February 11, 1994
		     Circulation This Issue: 213

Welcome to new members:

	Rex Wockner		(????????@??????.???)
