anyway. There was a pipe called "The Smoke" introduced in the 1960s,
which was made of pyrolitic graphite. It bombed... -S. ]


~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U ~\U

</pre>
