cigar!' Bogey. _Casablanca_. 1943. And Ingrid Bergman replies, `Why do
I only get that from guys who are lousy in bed?'"  

				- From "101 Ways to Answer the
				  Question, 'Would You Please Put Out
				  that #(!&amp;*!$ Cigar'," Hague et. al.,
