Subject: Pipes Digest #146 - June 9, 1994

		   Pipes Digest #146 - June 9, 1994
		     Circulation this issue: 383

*** LEGISLATIVE ALERT *** See Below

Welcome to new members:

	Jonathan A Cohen		(????@?????.???.???)
	Lynsa/MrHenry			(????????@????????.???)
	Jason Deines			(??????@???????.????????.???)
	???				(????@??????.???)
